high_descs: Turn right to face the stove.

Set the pan down on the white table.

Turn around, proceed to refrigerator on left.  Turn left and proceed to refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put pan on top shelf, close refrigerator.  Wait four seconds, remove pan from refrigerator and shut door.
Put pan on table, in front of egg and left of potato.
